<p>Hi everyone!</p>

<p>If you're reading this, you've received this email from the brand-new Backtracks 2.0! The platform as it previously existed was a piece of software I wrote in 2011, when I was a tiny baby, and it was extremely unreliable and hard to maintain. Some of you may have signed up and never gotten any emails, for which I heartily apologize!</p>

