<p>Just take a look at the email address that you received this via, and then go to this page and enter that address in order to get a password reset email: <a href="http://www.backtracks.co/recover_password">http://www.backtracks.co/recover_password</a></p>

<p>With the new website, I've got some other cool features in the works. If you're interested in hearing about things as they happen, you can follow Backtracks on Twitter at <a href="https://twitter.com/backtracks_co">@backtracks_co</a>.</p>

<p>Sorry for the huge long thing. Enjoy your charts and have a great day!</p>

